{"tid":779931,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇 Law Medic唔收Asso仔？","createTime":"2018-08-14T19:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T04:53:18.000Z","uid":112551,"like":28,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"15e68c9aab5e880fe1d984d3af88b3ae95f4c071","tid":779931,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T19:06:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.takungpao.com.hk/paper/q/2014/0707/2581929.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.takungpao.com.hk%2Fpaper%2Fq%2F2014%2F0707%2F2581929.html&d=7FOtiuBuuRuhu650SZRYby7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5d82d942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.takungpao.com.hk/paper/q/2014/0707/2581929.html</a><br />\n<br />\n港大法學院和中大法學院都稱，從沒有收錄法學副學士學生。城大法學院沒有透露收錄副學士數字。關注副學士大聯盟發言人馮偉華批評，根本不應該開辦這類專業課程，「為學生帶來假希望。」（見另稿）<br />\n<br />\nAsso仔爆4入Law Medic隨時屌打DSE IB狗，讀Law既再拎個LLB First Hon。<br />\n大學神科居然睇唔起Asso仔？明明DSE唔代表一切。"},{"pid":"2f76f435ec6786e86022366347ba3d07e106fce8","tid":779931,"uid":172376,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T19:08:51.000Z","msg":"係咁叻就唔洗讀asso上U啦"},{"pid":"e7d2c038274a22e6c9caf4defe3afb4362732fbb","tid":779931,"uid":198998,"like":40,"dislike":4,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T19:13:16.000Z","msg":"咁如果一個人dse得十幾分入asso 然後上到medic最後做到醫生 你敢唔敢比佢醫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054ad0be952807e58121dc9020c108c56e417555","tid":779931,"uid":112551,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2f76f435ec6786e86022366347ba3d07e106fce8","tid":779931,"uid":172376,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T19:08:51.000Z","msg":"係咁叻就唔洗讀asso上U啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T19:14:33.000Z","msg":"連大學都睇唔起Asso仔，唔信他日Become another person <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，Asso仔讀Law 一定爆4 拎Hon ，DSE反映唔到自己的能力。"},{"pid":"80a4b30d8a40ae4c33b3a5bd16ef9eff19697aa0"